instead of oatmeal. [ All Groaning ]

216
00:13:31,484 --> 00:13:34,195
Not again.
Howie.

217
00:13:34,195 --> 00:13:37,657
I have a suggestion, because there's
really, really not much time.

218
00:13:37,657 --> 00:13:40,868
I would like to propose
an essay contest...

219
00:13:40,868 --> 00:13:44,664
to decide once and for all
who will go with Prot.

220
00:13:44,664 --> 00:13:50,461
I've spoken with him, and he's
agreed to read them all by July 27.

221
00:13:50,461 --> 00:13:52,380
So if anyone would
like to be considered,

222
00:13:52,380 --> 00:13:55,716
please state your reasons
in a clear, legible hand...

223
00:13:55,716 --> 00:13:58,928
and return them to me.
[ Excited Chattering ]

224
00:13:58,928 --> 00:13:59,929
Russell.

225
00:14:02,223 --> 00:14:04,684
[ Chattering Continues ]
Yes?

226
00:14:06,978 --> 00:14:10,481
Would I get to take
my bible to K-PAX?

227
00:14:10,481 --> 00:14:12,900
Of course you would.

228
00:14:12,900 --> 00:14:15,862
[Betty] We can finish
the essays later.

229
00:14:23,536 --> 00:14:26,289
[Dr. Powell] Now, I want you
to go back in time again,

230
00:14:26,289 --> 00:14:28,624
