Your friend's name.

236
00:14:47,101 --> 00:14:49,604
Well, I ain't
gonna tell ya.

237
00:14:53,107 --> 00:14:56,235
Well, we have to
call him something.

238
00:14:56,235 --> 00:14:58,362
